---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Azrael Security">
  <section class="py-16">
    <h1 class="font-mono text-primary text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight mb-4">
      About
    </h1>

    <div class="text-text-muted max-w-2xl flex flex-col gap-4">
      <p>
        I am an offensive security engineer and vulnerability researcher operating under the Azrael Security brand. My work focuses on the boundary between userspace and kernel: container isolation failures, OCI runtime behavior, and the attack surface of GPU-enabled multi-tenant systems.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build the infrastructure I research on. Veil is a three-node WireGuard mesh I operate daily. NightForge is my operator workstation. Tairn runs live C2. The research comes from the infrastructure, not from synthetic labs.
      </p>
      <p>
        The tagline is below the abstraction. That is where the work happens.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-white/10 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ForeverLX"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="font-mono text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        GitHub
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ForeverLX/security-research"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="font-mono text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        Security Research
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/darrius-grate"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="font-mono text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-accent transition-colors"
      >
        LinkedIn
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
